        <item>
            <title>Casio 推出可爱治愈机械宠物 Moflin　内置 AI 可模拟感情并认出主人</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/13/casio-moflin-2/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=casio-moflin-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/13/casio-moflin-2/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 06:00:55 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CASIO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[宠物]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1268815</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>城市人生活紧张，有可爱宠物陪伴就可以治愈一下。Casio 最近就推出一款名为 Moflin 的机械宠物，毛茸茸的外形下还可以模拟情绪甚至认出主人。<br /><span id="more-1268815"></span></p><p>Casio 表示，随著时间 Moflin 可以逐渐学会识别主人，并尝试透过独特的声音和动作来发展模拟的情感连结。其设计宗旨是作为舒适的宠物伴侣，帮助改善心理健康，类似 Panasonic 的机械宠物 Nicobo。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_78211"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QBtdTTyF32Q?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>当被抱著时，Moflin 会透过头部和身体动作来互动，此外 Moflin 还具有一些 AI 功能，透过声音和处理方式识别最常与之互动的人，并以独特的声音和动作回应，经常互动会使它变得快乐、安全和平静，但如果被无视的话，可能会变得压力大、焦虑和悲伤。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268817" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/charaswiper_img4_png-694x470.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="470" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/charaswiper_img4_png-694x470.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/charaswiper_img4_png.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Moflin 充电的时候需要使用专属的「床铺」，在里面「睡眠」来充电，完全充电后可活动接近 5 小时，而充电则需要 3.5 小时。Moflin 售价为 59,400 日元，预计 11 月 7 日开始发售。Casio 还提供名为 Club Moflin 的可选订阅服务，年费 6,600 日元，包括维修、清洁服务，以及更换毛皮的折扣优惠。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268816" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/speccol1_imgsilver7_-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/speccol1_imgsilver7_-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/speccol1_imgsilver7_.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/speccol1_imgsilver7_-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.casio.com/jp/moflin/">Casio</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/12/nissan-gtr-themed-g-shock-watch/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Casio 与 Nissan 再次跨界联乘，全新 GT-R 主题 G-Shock 手表月中发表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/10/casio-cyberattack-g-shock-delay/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Casio 遭严重网络攻击，服务受阻 G-Shock 新表上市延期</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/05/g-shock-gundam-principality-of-zeon-watch-unveiled/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">自护限量版 G-Shock 发表，仅限 Gundam Fan Club 成员抽签购买</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/13/casio-moflin-2/life-tech/">Casio 推出可爱治愈机械宠物 Moflin　内置 AI 可模拟感情并认出主人</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
